												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Gale gestures with his hands, magically summoning a letter that hovers between him and the player. The player takes it and puts it away. (Reuse if we can/have to. Otherwise, for mocap - an elegant gesture with Gale's hands to 'draw' it into existence. Greg knows)"
